OL,3,CThe Lib Dem manifesto won't avoid
OL,4,Causterity in public services
OL,6,FThe Liberal Democrats promise a "fair
OL,7,Fdeal" for the United Kingdom which
OL,8,Fsounds reasonable, if not terribly
OL,9,Fexciting.
OL,11,FThe ambition is bold.
OL,13,F"Things in our country are broken,".
OL,14,FThe good news is the Lib Dems plan to
OL,15,Ffix things, everything: the economy,
OL,16,Fthe National Health Service, the
OL,17,Fclimate and the housing market.
