OL,3,CThe Lib Dem manifesto won't avoid
OL,4,Causterity in public services
OL,6,FOne way in which the Lib Dems say they
OL,7,Fwill do this is with a fairly big
OL,8,Fincrease - bigger than Labour looks
OL,9,Fset to propose in its manifesto.
OL,11,FSpending would rise by #26.8 billion a
OL,12,Fyear by the 2028/29.JHealth and social
OL,13,Fcare gets the lion's share of the
OL,14,Fextra money.
OL,16,F#8.3 billion would deliver 8,000 more
OL,17,FGPs, guaranteed access to an NHS
OL,18,Fdentist and improved.
OL,20,FBoosting the Carer's Allowance by #20
OL,21,Fa week will cost #1.4 billion.
