OL,6,FIn practice, the spending promises are
OL,7,Ffar more certain than tax proposals
OL,8,Fthe manifesto sets out.
OL,10,FThe Lib Dems hope to raise an extra
OL,11,F#26.8 billion a year by 2028/29,
OL,12,Fmostly from the very rich and larger
OL,13,Fcompanies.
