OL,3,CThe Lib Dem manifesto won't avoid
OL,4,Causterity in public services
OL,6,FThe idea of hitting unpopular
OL,7,Fcompanies with higher taxes will be
OL,8,Fpopular move but real people are
OL,9,Flikely to end up paying them.
OL,11,FBanks could respond to higher taxes
OL,12,Feither by charging more for their
OL,13,Fservices or cutting their costs. At
OL,14,Fthe margins, the unintended
OL,15,Fconsequences may be that savers get a
OL,16,Flittle less interest and borrowers pay
OL,17,Fa little more for a mortgage.
